00:14:38.000 --> 00:14:54.000
And what we look forward to and what we're going to talk through today is how Posit Team can sit alongside this data intelligence platform that Rafi's described and interact through a variety of different ways with that platform and leverage all the Databricks has to offer in terms of data governance.

00:14:55.000 --> 00:15:03.000
Governance, security, compute power, distributed computing, all the Databricks has to bring to the table, model serving, all these things that Rafi's touched on already.

