00:46:47.000 --> 00:46:53.000
So one of the advantages of Posit Connect is that it will define whatever environment I have locally,

00:46:53.000 --> 00:46:57.000
including the R packages and their versions and the Python packages and their versions.

00:46:57.000 --> 00:47:01.000
